---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout title="Typography Test - neprokin.com" description="Testing Typograf integration with Russian and English text">
	<section class="section">
		<div class="text-content">
			<h1 class="h1 text-accent mb-8">Typography Test</h1>
			<p class="body-large text-secondary mb-8">
				Testing Typograf integration with Russian and English text
			</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="section">
		<h2 class="h2 mb-6">Russian Typography</h2>
		
		<div class="text-content">
			<h3 class="body-large mb-4">Quotes and Dashes</h3>
			<p class="body mb-4">
				"Прямые кавычки" должны стать «типографскими кавычками». 
				А двойные дефисы -- должны стать — длинными тире.
			</p>

			<h3 class="body-large mb-4">Non-breaking Spaces</h3>
			<p class="body mb-4">
				Предлоги "в", "на", "с", "к" не должны оставаться в конце строки. 
				Например: "Путешествие в Италию" или "Работа на заводе".
			</p>

			<h3 class="body-large mb-4">Numbers and Units</h3>
			<p class="body mb-4">
				Числа и единицы измерения: 10 кг, 5 м, 100 руб, 25°C.
			</p>

			<h3 class="body-large mb-4">Abbreviations</h3>
			<p class="body mb-4">
				Сокращения: и т. д., т. е., н. э., А. С. Пушкин.
			</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="section">
		<h2 class="h2 mb-6">English Typography</h2>
		
		<div class="text-content">
			<h3 class="body-large mb-4">Quotes and Dashes</h3>
			<p class="body mb-4">
				"Straight quotes" should become "smart quotes". 
				Double dashes -- should become — em dashes.
			</p>

			<h3 class="body-large mb-4">Prepositions</h3>
			<p class="body mb-4">
				Short prepositions like "in", "on", "at", "to" should not break at line end.
				For example: "Travel in Italy" or "Work at factory".
			</p>

			<h3 class="body-large mb-4">Numbers and Units</h3>
			<p class="body mb-4">
				Numbers and units: 10 kg, 5 m, $100, 25°F.
			</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="section">
		<h2 class="h2 mb-6">Mixed Content</h2>
		
		<div class="text-content">
			<p class="body mb-4">
				Смешанный контент: "Hello world" на русском и "Привет мир" на английском.
				Numbers: 123 и 456, dates: 01.01.2024 и 12/31/2024.
			</p>

			<h3 class="body-large mb-4">Code Blocks (should not be processed)</h3>
			<pre class="body mb-4" style="background: var(--surface); padding: 16px; border-radius: 8px;">
<code>// This code should NOT be processed by Typograf
const text = "Hello world";
const number = 123;
</code>
			</pre>

			<h3 class="body-large mb-4">Inline Code (should not be processed)</h3>
			<p class="body mb-4">
				Inline code like <code>const x = 123;</code> should remain unchanged.
			</p>
		</div>
	</section>
</PageLayout>
